snippet.title: Train Chase - PCVR Trailer
snippet.description:
You're being chased by the enemy and have to escape.
Fight their drones, turrets and vehicles on a train through several levels and several waves.

Train Chase is a VR Rail Shooter that is available on Steam and Viveport. The update is scheduled for 21 of July, 2023.

Music: Crazy Drummer - By David Fesliyan
